### SQL Analyzer API 快速测试
### 核心功能验证

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 健康检查
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/ping

### 单条SQL分析 - 综合分析
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT u.name, COUNT(o.id) as order_count FROM users u LEFT JOIN orders o ON u.id = o.user_id WHERE u.status = 'active' GROUP BY u.id",
  "databaseType": "mysql",
  "options": {
    "performance": true,
    "security": true,
    "standards": true
  }
}

### 批量SQL分析
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analyze/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sqls": [
    "SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = 1",
    "UPDATE users SET last_login = NOW() WHERE id = 1"
  ],
  "databaseType": "mysql",
  "options": {
    "performance": true,
    "security": true
  }
}

### 安全分析测试
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = " + userInput,
  "databaseType": "mysql",
  "options": {
